import React from 'react';
import Login from './Login';
import { AppRoute } from './AppRoute'
import StatiquePage from './StatiquePage';
import Menu from './Menu'
import Magasins from './Magasins'
import AjoutMagasin from './AjoutMagasin'
import ExplMagasin from './ExplMagasin'
import ModifMagasin from './ModifMagasin'
import Articles from './Articles'
import ExplArticle from './ExplArticle'
import ModifArticle from './ModifArticle'
import AjoutArticle from './AjoutArticle'
import FamillesArt from './FamillesArt'
import AjoutFamille from './AjoutFamille'
import ModifFamille from './ModifFamille'

import { Link, BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Switch, withRouter } from 'react-router-dom'

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Switch>
        <AppRoute path="/ModifFamille" component={ModifFamille} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/AjoutFamille" component={AjoutFamille} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/ModifMagasin" component={ModifMagasin} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/AjoutMagasin" component={AjoutMagasin} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/AjoutArticle" component={AjoutArticle} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/ModifArticle" component={ModifArticle} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/FamillesArt" component={FamillesArt} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/ExplArticle" component={ExplArticle} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/ExplMagasin" component={ExplMagasin} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/Articles" component={Articles} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/Magasins" component={Magasins} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/Menu" component={Menu} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <Route path="/" render={() => <Login />} />
      </Switch>
    </Router>
  );
}

export default App;
